Scenario: verify default options for Priority Mail

And on the create label page I verify that Signature Confirmation option is enabled And on the create label page I verify that Signature Restricted Delivery option is enabled And on the create label page I verify that Insurance option is enabled And on the create label page I verify that Insurance Restricted Delivery option is enabled And on the create label page I verify that Certified Mail option is enabled And on the create label page I verify that Certified Mail Restricted Delivery option is enabled And on the create label page I verify that Registered Mail option is enabled And on the create label page I verify that Registered Restricted Delivery option is enabled And on the create label page I verify that Registered Insured Restricted Delivery option is enabled And on the create label page I verify that Return Receipt option is disabled And on the create label page I verify that Return Receipt Electronic option is disabled And on the create label page I verify that Fragile option is enabled And on the create label page I verify that Collect On Delivery option is enabled And on the create label page I verify that COD Restricted Delivery option is enabled And on the create label page I verify that total shipping price is 5.25 dollars
